description: Looking for easy lunch ideas? This delicious Italian beef and slaw sub recipe is perfect for days when you're on the go.
keywords: Sandwich,High fibre,High protein,Mince,Pork,Quick & easy lunch,Low sugar,Beef,Summer
name: Mexican Beef & Slaw Subs Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 300g BBQ Beef Mince Kebabs Mexican Style

recipeInstructions.text: Cook chips according to packet instructions.
Meanwhile, heat a barbecue grill on medium heat. Cook kebabs for 5 minutes on each side or until cooked through.
Split rolls, ensuring not to cut all the way through. Place coleslaw kit with dressing in a large bowl and toss to combine.
Place a little coleslaw in each roll. Remove skewers from kebabs and top each roll with a kebab. Serve with chips and any remaining coleslaw.
